{% extends "page.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Window Washing in Metro Vancouver BC | Clean Gutters Crew{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="window-section">

        <h1>2. Window Washing</h1>

        <img style="width: 100%" src="/assets/images/services/Windows.png">

        <h2>It Is More Than Just “For Looks”</h2>

        <p>
            Dirty windows can block up to 30–40% of natural light. That means:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Higher electricity bills</li>
            <li>More artificial lighting</li>
            <li>Reduced mood and comfort</li>
            <li>A constant “dirty home” feeling</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            In BC’s rainy environment, pollen, salt residue, and grime build up quickly.
        </p>

        <h2>Dangers of Ignoring It</h2>

        <p>Contaminants on glass include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Dust</li>
            <li>Pollen</li>
            <li>Acidic residues</li>
            <li>Bird droppings</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Over time this:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Scratches glass</li>
            <li>Damages seals</li>
            <li>Causes corrosion</li>
            <li>Contributes to mold growth</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Benefits of Regular Cleaning</h2>

        <ul>
            <li>More natural light</li>
            <li>Improved indoor air quality</li>
            <li>Protection of window seals</li>
            <li>Extended window lifespan</li>
            <li>Higher property value</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Psychological Effect</h2>

        <p>Natural light reduces stress.</p>
        <p>Bright interiors improve mood and sleep.</p>
        <p>Clean windows create a sense of order and control.</p>

        <h2>Table</h2>

        <div class="table-wrapper">
            <table class="service-table">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>If Ignored</th>
                    <th>What Happens</th>
                    <th>Regular Cleaning Provides</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Dirt buildup</td>
                    <td>Light blockage</td>
                    <td>Up to 40% more light</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Dust &amp; pollen</td>
                    <td>Allergens inside</td>
                    <td>Healthier air</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Bird droppings</td>
                    <td>Glass damage</td>
                    <td>Surface protection</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Moisture on frames</td>
                    <td>Mold growth</td>
                    <td>Seal integrity protection</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

    </section>
{% endblock %}

{% block styles %}
    <style>
        .window-section {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
        }

        .window-section h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .window-section h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .window-section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .window-section li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .table-wrapper {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .service-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            min-width: 600px;
        }

        .service-table thead {
            background: #f4f6f8;
        }

        .service-table th,
        .service-table td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .service-table th {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .service-table tbody tr:hover {
            background: #fafafa;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .window-section {
                padding: 25px 15px;
            }

            .window-section h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .window-section h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
{% endblock %}

